# ==========================================
# 修正版：确保能正确跟踪子目录内的文件
# ==========================================

# 1. 首先，忽略 Driver_Tester 目录下的所有东西
Driver_Tester/

# 2. 然后，强制保留 Driver_Tester 目录本身 (否则 git 会认为这是个空目录而忽略它)
!Driver_Tester/

# 3. 接着，重新忽略 Driver_Tester 下的所有文件 (递归)
Driver_Tester/**

# 4. 最后，白名单：显式保留需要的文件类型
!Driver_Tester/**/*.v
!Driver_Tester/**/*.sv
!Driver_Tester/**/*.qpf
!Driver_Tester/**/*.qsf
!Driver_Tester/**/*.sdc
!Driver_Tester/**/*.txt
!Driver_Tester/**/*.md
!Driver_Tester/**/*.pdf
!Driver_Tester/**/*.doc
!Driver_Tester/**/*.docx
!Driver_Tester/**/*.qip
!Driver_Tester/**/*.qsys
!Driver_Tester/**/*.mif
!Driver_Tester/**/*.hex